Please file this bug report at https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/new.

---

## What happened

Booting Android Studio after updating the Flutter plugin to work with the Android Studio Canary release.

## Version information

Android Studio `Chipmunk | 2021.2.1 Canary 5` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 62.0.3` • Dart plugin `212.5632`

No Flutter sdk configured.
